  https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getElementById

- Element.className()
  https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/className

- Element.classList()
  https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/classList
- Toggle
  document.querySelector("main li:first-child").classList.remove("new-class")
  on and off (True and False)

- Element.attributes
  https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/attributes
- Has Key and Value
- Can manipulate Key and Value
- has
  document.querySelector("img").hasAttribute("src")
- get
  document.querySelector("img").getAttribute("src")
- set
  document.querySelector("img").setAttribute("alt", "A Drawing of a Backpack")
- remove
  document.querySelector("img").removeAttribute("alt", "A Drawing of a Backpack")

